                <p>Part 12B FSMA and regulations 2 and 4 of the Capital Requirements Regulations 2013/3115 as well as existing provisions in the Banking Act 2009 c.1 and sections 64 and 65 of the Financial Services Act 2012 c.21</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Regulations 2 and 4 </p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p />
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
