                <p>Updates to requirements applicable to the EBA with regards to credit institutions authorisation</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p><b>No implementation needed – </b>requirements applicable to the EBA</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Not applicable</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p />
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                <p>Article 9</p>
