                <p>Updates to prohibition against persons or undertakings other than credit institutions from carrying out the business of taking deposits or other repayable funds from the public</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p><b>No implementation needed - </b>UK law already provides for this </p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Not applicable</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p />
