                <p>Regulations 1, 35, 50, 51, 52, 53, 53, 56, 57, 58, 58 and 59 of the Capital Requirements (Amendment) (EU Exit) Regulations 2018 – which amend regulations 2, 22, 23, 24, 25, 27, 30, 31, 32, 34 and 35 of the Capital Requirements (Capital Buffers and Macro-prudential Measures) Regulations 2014</p>
